8 Bits to Infinity 
presents 
PUZZLE JAM

Theme: Black & White
Sub-theme (for Weekly Game Jam): 100

Color Palette: obviously black and white

Titles:
- Josh has 100 Seconds to Escape!
-- 100 Seconds to Escape
- 100 Seconds of Josh
- 100 Seconds <-- CHOSEN TITLE

These videos will help: 
- What Makes a Good Puzzle?: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsjC6fa_YBg
- Puzzle Solving... or Problem Solving?: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w1_zmx-wU0U
- How Jonathan Blow Designs a Puzzle: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2zK8ItePe3Y
- Puzzle Games - Analyzing the Design of Bejeweled - Extra Credits: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZKD5eOIXY08

music: I will use Joshua McLean's musics.
- http://mrjoshuamclean.com/royalty-free-music/

arts: I will use most of assets from OpenGameArt.org.
